  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "15. Because the law worketh wrath—has nothing to give to those who break is but condemnation and vengeance.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "for where there is no law, there is no transgression—It is just the law that makes transgression, in the case of those who break it; nor can the one exist without the other.",
        "children": []
      }
